---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Nick: software engineer, game jam enthusiast, and Visualization Master's student"
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		I'm Nick, a software engineer from Bergen, Norway. I graduated with a Bachelor's in Computing (Software Development) from Western Norway University of Applied Sciences (HVL) in 2021, and I'm currently in my second semester of a Master's in Informatics (Visualization) at the <a href="https://www4.uib.no/en/studies/programmes/informatics-masters/plan-7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">University of Bergen (UiB)</a>.
	</p>

	<p>
		I worked as a Full Stack Engineer at InkyPen AS from Sep. 2023 until Aug. 2025, where I contributed to B2B and B2C digital distribution platforms for comics and manga. I have experience with AWS, .NET, React/TypeScript, and Unity. I've also been a Group Leader for INF214 (Concurrent programming) at UiB and a Student Assistant at HVL.
	</p>

	<p>
		I'm always interested in new technologies and solutions, enjoy working in diverse teams, and I'm not afraid to ask questions. I've participated in Bergen Game Jam three times (volunteered twice), three Ludum Dare jams, and I'm a Volunteer Coordinator & Assistant-Webmaster for Konsoll (Game Development Conference). Some of my game jam projects are on <a href="https://nickmarcha.itch.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">nickmarcha.itch.io</a>.
	</p>

	<p>
		<strong>Contact</strong><br />
		<a href="mailto:nicolasmmjoes@outlook.com">nicolasmmjoes@outlook.com</a><br />
		Bergen, Norway
	</p>

	<p>
		<strong>Languages:</strong> Norwegian (native), Spanish (fluent), English (fluent), German (good command)
	</p>
</Layout>
